# Planner Component

The `Planner` component provides a comprehensive scheduling and resource management interface. It displays appointments, events, or tasks in a timeline view, allowing users to visualize and manage schedules across different resources like people, rooms, or equipment. The component supports drag-and-drop interactions, appointment creation, and various view options.

