## Usage Example

Here's a basic usage example of the `Planner`:

```tsx
<Canvas>
  <Story name="Default">
    <Planner
      appointments={[
        {
          id: "1",
          title: "Project Meeting",
          startDate: new Date(2023, 5, 15, 10, 0),
          endDate: new Date(2023, 5, 15, 11, 30),
          resourceId: "1"
        },
        {
          id: "2",
          title: "Client Call",
          startDate: new Date(2023, 5, 15, 14, 0),
          endDate: new Date(2023, 5, 15, 15, 0),
          resourceId: "2"
        }
      ]}
      resources={[
        { id: "1", title: "Conference Room A" },
        { id: "2", title: "Conference Room B" },
        { id: "3", title: "Meeting Room 101" }
      ]}
      currentDate={new Date(2023, 5, 15)}
      height={600}
      onAppointmentAdd={(data) => console.info("New appointment:", data)}
      onAppointmentChange={(data) => console.info("Changed appointment:", data)}
      onAppointmentDelete={(id) => console.info("Deleted appointment:", id)}
    />
  </Story>
</Canvas>
``` 